  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.4">
<l>pañciyamel laṭippiṉṉai tiṟattu muṉṉāḷ pāyviṭaika ḷēḻaṭarttu poṉṉaṉ paimpūṇ</l>
<l>neñciṭantu kurutiyuka vukirvē lāṇṭa niṉmalaṉṟā ḷaṇaikiṟpīr nīla mālait</l>
<l>tañcuṭaiya viruḷtaḻaippat taraḷa māṅkē taṇmatiyiṉ nilākkāṭṭap pavaḷan taṉṉāl</l>
<l>ceñcuṭarve yilvirikku maḻakār kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would touch the feet of the pure lord who used claw weapons</l>
<l rend="indent">so that blood scattered, gouging out the fine jeweled chest</l>
<l rend="indent">of the golden one,</l>
<l>Having long ago destroyed seven leaping bulls for the sake of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with cotton[-like] soft feet,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in beautiful Kāḻi</l>
<l rend="indent">where the rosy rays of sun[set] are lengthened by corals,</l>
<l>As pearls there display the cool moon’s beams,</l>
<l rend="indent">and as sapphires intensify the protective darkness of evening.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
